resources.string: "Lokhu kusula ulwazi olusetshenziselwe ukuxhuma kule nethiwekhi, kufaka phakathi iphasiwedi eilondoloziwe"

"Lolu hlu lokukhetha alivumelekile. Faka uhlu oluhlukaniswe ngekhoma lwezizinda ezikhishiwe."
"Uma inkambu yosokhaya ingenalutho, shiya inkambu yembobo ingenalutho"
"Ummeleli we-HTTP usetshenziswa isiphequluli kodwa ngeke isetshenziswe ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza"
"Faka uhlu oluhlukaniswe ngekhoma lezizinda ezikhishiwe noma shiya kungenalutho.\nIsibonelo: example.com,mycomp.test.com,localhost"

"Ukuze usebenzise izinhlelo zokusebenza noma idatha ekule drayivu, ixhume kabusha. Ngokunye, ungakwazi ukukhetha ukukhohlwa lesi sitoreji uma idrayivu ingatholakali.

Uma ukhetha ukukhohlwa, yonke idatha equkethwe idrayivu izolahleka unaphakade.

Ungaka kabusha izinhlelo zokusebenza emuva kwesikhathi, kodwa idatha elondolozwe kule drayivu izolahleka."

"Lokhu kudinga ukuthi idrayivu ye-USB ifomethwe ukuze yenziwe ivikeleke. Ngemuva kokufometha ngokuphephile, le drayivu izosebenza kuphela ngale divayisi. Ukufometha kususa yonke idatha okwamanje egcinwe kudrayivu. Ukuze ugweme ukulahlekelwa yidatha, cabanga ngokwenza isipele."
"Ngemuva kokufometha, ungasebenzisa le drayivu ye-USB kwamanye amadivayisi. Yonke idatha izosulwa. Cabanga ngokwenza isipele kuqala ngokuhambisa izinhlelo zokusebenza kwesinye isitoreji sedivayisi."
"Hambisa izithombe zakho, amafayela nedatha yohlelo lokusebenza ku-%1$s. Lokhu kungathatha amaminithi ambalwa. Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ngeke zisebenze ngokulungile ngesikhathi sokuhanjiswa."
"Lokhu kungathatha isikhathi. Sicela ungasusi idrayivu.\nEzinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ngeke zisebenze ngokulungile ngesikhathi sokuhanjiswa."

"Ungaqhubeka, kodwa izinhlelo zokusebenza eziyiswe kule ndawo singahle zingasheshi futhi ukudluliswa kwedatha kungathatha isikhathi eside. Naka ukusebenzisa idrayivu esheshayo ngokusebenza okungcono."
"Izinhlelo zokusebenza kulesi sitoreji sale divayisi zizomisa ukusebenza uma ikhishwa. Le drayivu ye-USB ifomethwe ukuze isebenze kule divayisi kuphela. Ngeke ize isebenze kunoma yimaphi amanye"
"Ungasusi idrayivu ngesikhathi sokuhambisa.\nUhlelo lokusebenza lwe-%1$s kule divayisi ngeke luze lutholakale kuze kuqedwe ukuhambisa."
"Yonke idatha yakho elondolozwe kule drayivu izolahleka unaphakade ngokuthi \'Khohlwa\'. Ungathanda ukuqhubeka?"
"Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ngeke zitholakale noma ngeke zisebenze kahle idrayivu ize ixhunywe kabusha."
"Vumela izinhlelo zokusebenza ezicele imvume yakho ukusebenzisa ulwazi lendawo yakho"
"Azikho izinhlelo zokusebenza ezicele indawo kamuva nje"

"I-Google isebenzisa lesi sici emikhiqizweni njenge-Google Now ne-Google Amamephu. Ukuvula ukubikwa kwendawo kuvumela noma yimuphi umkhiqizo we-Google esebenzisa lesi sici igcina futhi isebenzise idatha yakho yendawo yakamuva yedivayisi ngokuxhumana ne-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google."

"Uma umlando wedawo uvuliwe kule akhawunti, i-Google ingagcina idatha yakho yendawo yedivayisi ukuze usetshenziswe izinhlelo zakho zokusebenza.

Isibonelo, i-Google Amamephu ikunika izinkombhandlela, futhi i-Google Now ingakwazisa mayelana nethrafikhi yokuhamba.

Ungavala umlando wendawo noma kunini, kodwa ukwenza kanjalo akuyisusi. Ukuze ubuke futhi uphathe umlando wendawo yakho, vakashela ku-maps.google.com/locationhistory."

"Lokhu kuzosusa wonke umlando wendawo obekwe kusuka kule divayisi yale-akhawunti ye-Google. Awukwazi ukuhlehlisa lokhu kususwa. Ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza, okufaka phakathi i-Google Now, kuzomisa ukusebenza."
"Uma isinqamuleli sivuliwe, ungacindezela zombili izinkinobho ezingemuva neziphansi ngamasekhondi angu-3 ukuze uqale isici sokufinyelela."
"I-%1$s ingaqoqa wonke umbhalo owuthayiphayo, ngaphandle kwamaphasiwedi. Lokhu kufaka idatha yomuntu siqu efana nezinombolo zekhadi lesikweletu."
"Ukuze ubuyekeze lesi silungiselelo, idivayisi yakho idinga ukuqaliswa kabusha"
"Hlola izinhlelo zokusebenza ezifakiwe nge-ADB/ADT ngokuziphatha okuyingozi"
"Thuthukisa ukubuka ngokucacisa okuphezulu noma isilinganiso sefremu esikhulu. Lokhu kuthinta kuphela izibonisi ze-Ultra HD. Ukushintsha lesi silungiselelo kuzoqala kabusha idivayisi yakho."

"Ukubuka okukhanyayo phakathi kwamawindi uma kudwetshwe nge-GPU"
"Kusuka kokuhle kuya kokubi kakhulu: okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, okuluhlaza okotshani, okubomvu okukhanyayo, okubomvu"
"Khanyisa ukubonakala kwalo lonke iwindi uma libuyekezwa"
"Khanyisa isikrini uma izinhlelo zokusebenza zenza umsebenzi ngesikhathi eside kuchungechunge olukhulu"

"Idivayisi yakho nedatha yomuntu siqu ivuleleke kakhulu ekuhlaselweni yizinhlelo zokusebenza ezisuka kumithombo engaziwa. Uyavuma ukuthi nguwe kuphela onesibopho sanoma yikuphi ukulimala kudivayisi yakho noma ukulahlekelwa yidatha okungasuka kusukela ekusebenziseni lezi zinhlelo zokusebenza."

"Uma uphoqelela ukuma kuhlelo lokusebenza, kungenzeka lingaziphathi kahle."
"Zonke izibuyekezo kulolu hlelo lokusebenza lwesistimu ye-Android zizokhishwa."
"Yonke le datha yohlelo lokusebenza izozuswa unaphakade.\nLokhu kufaka phakathi wonke amafayela, izilungiselelo, ama-akhawunti, imininingo egciniwe, njll."

"Isilondolozi sesikrini siqala ngemuva kwalesi sikhathi sokungasebenzi. Uma singekho isilondolozi sesikrini esikhethiwe, isibonisi siyacisha."
"Ayikho i-akhawunti okwamanje elondoloza idatha eyenziwe isipele"
"Yeka ukwenza isipele amaphasiwedi wakho we-Wi-Fi, amabhukhimakhi, ezinye izilungiselelo, kanye nedatha yohlelo lokusebenza,futhi ususe wonke amakhophi kumaseva we-Google?"

"Lokhu kuzosula yonke idatha kusukela kusitoreji sedivayisi yakho sangaphakathi, okufaka: i-akhawunti yakho ye-Google, idatha yesistimu neyohlelo lokusebenza nezilungiselelo, nezinhlelo zokusebenza ezilandiwe"

"Nikeza idivayisi yakho igama ukuze usize ukuyikhomba ngenkathi usakaza noma uyixhuma kusukela kwamanye amadivayisi."
"Sebenzisa leli gama uma usakaza izithombe, amavidiyo, nokuningi kusukela kufoni yakho"
"Lokhu kuzokhubaza zonke izinhlelo zokusebenza zenkampani yangaphandle oyifakile. Kuzobuyiselwa uma uphinda uqalisa futhi."

"Ukufinyelela kokusebenzisa kuvumela uhlelo lokusebenza ukuthi lulandelele ukuthi yiziphi ezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ozisebenzisayo nokuthi kaningi kangakanani, kanye nenkampani yakho yenethiwekhi, izilungiselelo zolimi neminye imininingwane."

"Lezi zinhlelo zokusebenza zizokwazi ukufunda zonke izaziso, kufaka phakathi ulwazi lomuntu siqu njengamagama woxhumana nabo nombhalo womlayezo owutholayo. Azokwazi ukulahla izaziso noma icuphe izinkinobho zesenzo ezinawo."

"Vumela uhlelo lokusebenza ukuthi luboniswe ngaphezulu kwezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza ozisebenzisayo. Lingaphazamisana nokusebenza kwalezo zinhlelo zokusebenza noma lishintshe indlela ezibonakala zivela ngayo noma eziziphatha ngayo."
"Le mvume ivumela uhlelo lokusebenza ukushintsha izilungiselelo zesistimu."
"Azikho izinhlelo zokusebenza ezifakiwe ezisekela isithombe phakathi kwesithombe"
